OL,3,CStarmer to face questions in Commons
OL,4,Cfor first time since Mandelson arrest
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer is expected to face
OL,7,Fquestions from MPs in the Commons for
OL,8,Fthe first time since the arrest of
OL,9,FLord Peter Mandelson.
OL,11,FThe former ambassador to Washington
OL,12,Fwas arrested on Monday on suspicion of
OL,13,Fmisconduct in public office and later
OL,14,Freleased on bail.
OL,16,FLord Mandelson, who has been accused
OL,17,Fof passing sensitive information onto
OL,18,Fpaedophile financier Jeffrey Epstein
OL,19,Fduring his time as business secretary,
OL,20,Fhas been bailed until May.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
