OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1772019653
OL,3,CStarmer to face questions in Commons
OL,4,Cfor first time since Mandelson arrest
OL,6,FThey said: "There is absolutely no
OL,7,Ftruth whatsoever in any such
OL,8,Fsuggestion. We have asked the MPS
OL,9,F(Metropolitan Police Service) for the
OL,10,Fevidence relied upon to justify the
OL,11,Farrest.
OL,13,F"Peter Mandelson's overriding priority
OL,14,Fis to co-operate with the police
OL,15,Finvestigation, as he has done
OL,16,Fthroughout this process, and to clear
OL,17,Fhis name."
OL,26,@nD@LOUuD@AOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
