OL,3,CStarmer to face questions in Commons
OL,4,Cfor first time since Mandelson arrest
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police declined to
OL,7,Fcomment beyond their statement issued
OL,8,Fjust after 2am on Tuesday, which read:
OL,9,F"A 72-year-old man arrested on
OL,10,Fsuspicion of misconduct in public
OL,11,Foffice has been released on bail
OL,12,Fpending further investigation."
OL,14,FLord Mandelson was taken into custody
OL,15,Fafter Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor's
OL,16,Farrest last week, also on suspicion of
OL,17,Fmisconduct in public office, after
OL,18,Fallegations he shared sensitive
OL,19,Finformation with Epstein during his
OL,20,Ftime as the UK's trade envoy.
OL,26,@qD@AOUtD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
