OL,3,CStarmer to face questions in Commons
OL,4,Cfor first time since Mandelson arrest
OL,6,FAnd one of Starmer's ministers took
OL,7,Faim at Andrew in the Commons on
OL,8,FTuesday, calling him a "rude, arrogant
OL,9,Fand entitled man" who was on a
OL,10,F"constant self-aggrandising and self-
OL,11,Fenriching hustle".
OL,13,FAndrew spent 11 hours in custody after
OL,14,Fhis arrest on his 66th birthday.
OL,15,FPolice confirmed on Tuesday night they
OL,16,Fhad completed searches at Andrew's
OL,17,Fformer home, Royal Lodge.
OL,26,@pD@XOUqD@QO]rD@AOUsD@QO]
